sure sensitivity, so you can quickly go between thick or thinner lines and different degrees of shading depending on the pressure on the stylus.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You might also be wondering how this Apple Pencil is over half off the typical price. That’s because it’s a new open-box model! It’s in new condition, but it may have had customer contact, or its packaging may have extra signs of handling.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sketch and write intuitively on your iPad when you grab this <a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=111346X1569486&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/apple-pencil-usb-c-muwa3am-a-new-open-box?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=apple-pencil-usb-c-muwa3am-a-new-open-box&amp;utm_term=scsf-599654&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000001ZkLxIAK&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2375568-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">new, open-box Apple Pencil for just $59.99</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=111346X1569486&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/apple-pencil-usb-c-muwa3am-a-new-open-box?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral-cta&amp;utm_campaign=apple-pencil-usb-c-muwa3am-a-new-open-box&amp;utm_term=scsf-599654&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000001ZkLxIAK&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2375568-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://cdnp3.stackassets.com/ee1813621fb6318e0bdce8f601bdb49bbca6564e/store/1cd9dd86adc722a55d09f3c6e28809102cc91486cd9db83149d23ba5c436/40d25de9-8579-5e26-bbbd-8944817aa67a.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" /></figure></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" /></figure></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>New Open-Box Apple Pencil (USB-C)</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.skimresources